# Futuristic Developer Portfolio — Sai Sundar

A modern futuristic portfolio with glassmorphism, animated gradients, neon UI, smooth scrolling, and scroll reveal effects.

---

# Folder Structure

```bash
portfolio/
│
├── index.html
├── style.css
├── script.js
├── images/
│   ├── profile.png
│   └── project-images
```

---

